1
00:01:12,040 --> 00:01:13,719
You don't bask in the moonlight,

2
00:01:14,040 --> 00:01:15,280
but you don't need to turn off the lights.

3
00:01:16,280 --> 00:01:16,840
I forgot it.

4
00:01:20,920 --> 00:01:22,120
Why is your face so red?

5
00:01:22,560 --> 00:01:24,280
Are you having a fever?

6
00:01:24,359 --> 00:01:24,959
No.

7
00:01:27,799 --> 00:01:28,319
What are you doing here?

8
00:01:29,640 --> 00:01:31,480
I'm here to see if you are hiding well.

9
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:33,159
In case you go out and get into trouble.

10
00:01:35,079 --> 00:01:35,719
Where is my brother?

11
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:39,280
There's a disturbance at the lighthouse port.

12
00:01:39,359 --> 00:01:40,200
He went to deal with it.

13
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:43,879
But tonight,

14
00:01:44,359 --> 00:01:46,239
he can control his body better than others.

15
00:01:46,799 --> 00:01:48,200
If he's not directly exposed to the moonlight,

16
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:49,599
he won't be hurt.

17
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:53,439
No.

18
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:54,680
I should go find him.

19
00:01:55,079 --> 00:01:56,760
Four fists are better than two, right?

20
00:01:57,400 --> 00:01:58,680
Don't make things worse.

21
00:01:59,079 --> 00:02:00,040
Don't let others catch you

22
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:01,120
and save you.

23
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:06,959
Every time I'm set up,

24
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:08,639
it's because

25
00:02:08,719 --> 00:02:10,719
by your trick?

26
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:13,159
I'm sorry.

27
00:02:16,199 --> 00:02:16,639
What?

28
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:18,400
I didn't hear you. Louder.

29
00:02:19,039 --> 00:02:19,599
Nothing.

30
00:02:20,319 --> 00:02:20,919
I'm going to bed.

31
00:02:22,080 --> 00:02:22,879
Stubborn.

32
00:02:27,479 --> 00:02:28,599
Don't go out.

33
00:03:06,199 --> 00:03:07,360
Where are you in such a hurry to go?

34
00:03:08,199 --> 00:03:09,400
The wolf has been returned to the mountains.

35
00:03:09,719 --> 00:03:10,759
You still miss him so much.

36
00:03:11,719 --> 00:03:14,199
So you deliberately made trouble to lure him out.

37
00:03:14,639 --> 00:03:15,240
I've said

38
00:03:15,879 --> 00:03:17,479
I have plenty of ways to take you home.

39
00:03:17,879 --> 00:03:18,719
I've also said

40
00:03:19,599 --> 00:03:21,199
I have the right to choose.

41
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:23,240
If being with a murderer

42
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:24,439
is your so-called freedom,

43
00:03:24,919 --> 00:03:26,080
then as your brother,

44
00:03:26,639 --> 00:03:28,280
I really don't know if I should interfere.

45
00:03:28,479 --> 00:03:29,199
What do you mean?

46
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,719
A mad dog barking.

47
00:03:38,159 --> 00:03:40,080
So your real purpose in coming to this island

48
00:03:41,039 --> 00:03:41,759
is to find

49
00:03:41,759 --> 00:03:43,479
about your mother's disappearance, right?

50
00:03:43,759 --> 00:03:45,039
Why did you read my notebook?

51
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:46,960
You're invading my privacy.

52
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:47,879
Moon,

53
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:49,280
if you had told me earlier,

54
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:50,639
I could have helped you sooner.

55
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:53,000
The photo of the real killer

56
00:03:53,639 --> 00:03:54,319
is right here.

57
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:01,319
On the day you got into trouble,

58
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:02,479
Lu Zhiyu was also at

59
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,639
Qin Yeren's shop.

60
00:04:05,599 --> 00:04:06,919
You should know better than I do

61
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:08,680
than I do.

62
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:11,159
I've asked him for the truth.

63
00:04:12,159 --> 00:04:13,000
Silly girl.

64
00:04:13,439 --> 00:04:14,360
A murderer.

65
00:04:14,439 --> 00:04:15,960
What truth do you expect from him?

66
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:19,240
He and Qin Yeren met in secret a few days ago.

67
00:04:19,959 --> 00:04:20,959
I happened to see them.

68
00:04:26,959 --> 00:04:28,560
You didn't come back last night.

69
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:30,439
Zhang San and Li Si were not there either.

70
00:04:31,879 --> 00:04:33,079
I took them hunting.

71
00:04:36,199 --> 00:04:37,199
The truth is obvious.

72
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:39,000
You are just their prey.

73
00:04:40,079 --> 00:04:42,160
So you told me all this on the night of the full moon

74
00:04:42,439 --> 00:04:43,600
to lure him

75
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:44,879
and expose his identity, right?

76
00:04:45,639 --> 00:04:46,759
This is a golden opportunity.

77
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:49,560
According to historical records,

78
00:04:49,959 --> 00:04:51,160
when the wolf clan transforms,

79
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:52,959
their blood circulation accelerates.

80
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:54,920
Compared to human body functions,

81
00:04:55,399 --> 00:04:56,800
he is more similar to a wolf dog.

82
00:05:03,319 --> 00:05:05,240
This is a muscle degrading agent with theobromine.

83
00:05:05,839 --> 00:05:07,279
It can temporarily deplete his physical strength,

84
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:09,079
making it easier for you to question him.

85
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:14,879
Don't you wanna avenge your mom?

86
00:05:16,959 --> 00:05:17,959
I don't need

87
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:20,160
to do this to find the truth.

88
00:05:21,279 --> 00:05:22,759
I know Lu Zhiyu better than you do.

89
00:05:23,399 --> 00:05:24,759
I won't hurt him

90
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:26,319
before I find the truth.

91
00:05:30,879 --> 00:05:31,759
Let me go!

92
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:58,360
Sorry.

93
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:01,240
I have to take you home this way.

94
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:04,040
You smell like

95
00:07:05,199 --> 00:07:06,040
motor oil.

96
00:07:07,759 --> 00:07:09,199
Looks like Qin Yeren can't sit still.

97
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:11,560
Come on.

98
00:07:12,879 --> 00:07:13,639
Tell me

99
00:07:13,839 --> 00:07:16,000
the route of his smuggling tonight

100
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:17,040
and the code.

101
00:07:18,839 --> 00:07:20,199
I can spare your life.

102
00:07:36,639 --> 00:07:38,079
The drug will wear off soon.

103
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:39,600
Now you just

104
00:07:40,079 --> 00:07:41,839
stay put.

105
00:07:47,079 --> 00:07:47,879
I'm sorry

106
00:07:48,759 --> 00:07:50,199
that I can't let you say goodbye

107
00:07:50,319 --> 00:07:50,959
to your animal friends.

108
00:07:53,079 --> 00:07:55,279
Is it the direction to the airport?

109
00:07:56,279 --> 00:07:57,759
The airport is crowded and complicated.

110
00:07:58,720 --> 00:08:01,000
Didn't you say you wanted to take a helicopter when you were little?

111
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:03,480
I'll take you to experience it in a while.

112
00:08:21,519 --> 00:08:22,319
Damn it!

113
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:23,959
How come I haven't been caught yet?

114
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:56,600
No!

115
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:32,480
Lu Zhiyu!

116
00:09:34,919 --> 00:09:35,519
Lu Zhiyu!

117
00:09:36,919 --> 00:09:37,759
Lu Zhiyu!

118
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:51,120
Stay away from me!

119
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:56,039
As long as you don't leave me,

120
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:58,679
I won't give up on you either.

121
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:01,279
I will soon become a stranger to you.

122
00:11:45,799 --> 00:11:47,720
We are partners for life.

123
00:11:48,559 --> 00:11:49,720
No matter how you change,

124
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:53,440
you will definitely recognize me.

125
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:29,919
Where are we?

126
00:12:31,559 --> 00:12:33,080
In a place where others can't find.

127
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:35,039
I...

128
00:12:36,159 --> 00:12:37,200
I didn't bite anyone last night, did I?

129
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:40,080
Yesterday was Christmas Eve.

130
00:12:40,679 --> 00:12:41,840
No one was hurt.

131
00:12:49,159 --> 00:12:49,759
It's nothing.

132
00:12:50,240 --> 00:12:51,240
Got scratched by a branch.

133
00:13:12,279 --> 00:13:12,759
By the way,

134
00:13:13,440 --> 00:13:14,759
how did you know where I was yesterday?

135
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:17,480
The power of the tide

136
00:13:18,360 --> 00:13:19,799
sharpens my senses.

137
00:13:20,639 --> 00:13:21,679
Even in a crowd,

138
00:13:22,679 --> 00:13:23,440
I can find you.

139
00:13:27,279 --> 00:13:27,799
Let's go.

140
00:13:41,159 --> 00:13:42,000
Last night, my men

141
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:43,159
surrounded the troublemakers.

142
00:13:43,919 --> 00:13:44,919
Those thugs surrendered.

143
00:13:45,399 --> 00:13:46,080
Let's go home.

144
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:47,279
There's a victory feast today.

145
00:13:50,120 --> 00:13:51,080
Let's go home together.
